---
// Three Steps Section
---

<section id="three-steps" class="py-24 px-6 bg-surface border-t border-border" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:steps">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:container">
    <div class="text-center mb-16" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:header">
      <h2 class="text-[48px] font-bold font-serif text-secondary mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:st6cuw">
        Three Steps to <span class="text-primary italic font-normal" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:ppex1q">I Do</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:ht2udp">Planning a destination wedding shouldn't be stressful. We've simplified the journey so you can focus on the celebration.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-24" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:grid-steps">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="text-center" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:step-1">
        <div class="relative w-20 h-20 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm mx-auto mb-8" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:5uhhgx">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/></svg>
          <div class="absolute -top-1 -right-1 w-7 h-7 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs shadow-md" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:5uhhgy">1</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-secondary mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:q2phu6">Find Your Vibe</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:ht2udq">Use our intuitive filters to browse venues by destination, vibe, and budget. Narrow down your favourites in minutes.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="text-center" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:step-2">
        <div class="relative w-20 h-20 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm mx-auto mb-8" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:5uhhgz">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          <div class="absolute -top-1 -right-1 w-7 h-7 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs shadow-md" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:5uhhh0">2</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-secondary mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:q2phu7">Expert Consultation</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:ht2udr">Speak to our dedicated planners. We'll verify availability, check legal requirements, and fine-tune your shortlist.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="text-center" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:step-3">
        <div class="relative w-20 h-20 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm mx-auto mb-8" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:5uhhh1">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.382-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z"/></svg>
          <div class="absolute -top-1 -right-1 w-7 h-7 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs shadow-md" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:5uhhh2">3</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-secondary mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:q2phu8">Tailored Planning</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:ht2uds">Once you've chosen your venue, we handle all the logistics, from legal paperwork to travel bookings for you and your guests.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mini Testimonials Row -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 border-t border-border pt-16" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:mini-quotes">
      <div class="text-center" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:5uhhh3">
        <p class="text-sm italic font-serif text-secondary mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:ht2udt">"The Wedding Travel Company found us a venue we never would have discovered on our own. Our Lake Como wedding was absolute perfection."</p>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:ppex1r">— EMMA & DAVID, ITALY</span>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:5uhhh4">
        <p class="text-sm italic font-serif text-secondary mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:ht2udu">"Planning from the UK felt daunting until we met our specialist. Every detail was handled with so much care and expertise."</p>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:ppex1s">— SARAH & TOM, MEXICO</span>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:5uhhh5">
        <p class="text-sm italic font-serif text-secondary mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:ht2udv">"Truly the best decision we made. They matched our 'boho' vibe perfectly and took all the legal stress away from us."</p>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground" data-ps="src/components/home/ThreeSteps.astro:ppex1t">— CHLOE & JACK, GREECE</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
